              },
              "free_text": [
                " The uncertainty for the data comes from the",
                " combination of the following factors-",
                " a) errors in the transmission values due to",
                "    counting statistics and background subtraction,",
                " B) the uncertainty of area determination in the",
                "    resonance analysis,",
                " C) systematic errors deduced from the fluctuation",
                "    between different sets of parameters,",
                " d) the error due to the fact that gamma width varies",
                "    slightly from level to level, and",
                " e) the error due to the use of the Breit-Wigner",
                "    single level formula."
              ]
            }
